00:12:22.890 --> 00:12:24.660 align:middle line:84%
the answer back
into the equation

00:12:24.660 --> 00:12:28.650 align:middle line:84%
so that you have an
iteration process.

00:12:28.650 --> 00:12:31.530 align:middle line:10%
And so you can imagine--
like, for instance--

00:12:31.530 --> 00:12:35.490 align:middle line:10%
