replication of the pattern

00:13:31.540 --> 00:13:33.630 align:middle line:90%
at many different scales.

00:13:33.630 --> 00:13:37.510 align:middle line:84%
And you see that in
nature very much so.

00:13:37.510 --> 00:13:40.939 align:middle line:84%
Fractal mathematics are
